Q :(-\epsilon,\epsilon) \to Aff_n(\mathbb R)
\forall A:(-\epsilon,\epsilon) \to GL_n(\mathbb R), A(0) = id_n
\forall b \in \mathbb{R}^n
Q(t) =\begin{pmatrix}         A(t) & \ bt \\         0 & 1 \\         \end{pmatrix}
\dot Q(t) =\begin{pmatrix}         \dot A(t) & \ b \\         0 & 0 \\         \end{pmatrix}
\dot Q(0) =\begin{pmatrix}         \dot A(0) & \ b \\         0 & 0 \\         \end{pmatrix} \in \mathfrak{aff}(n) 
\implies \mathfrak{aff}(n) =  \{ \begin{pmatrix}         M & \ b \\         0 & 0 \\         \end{pmatrix} \mid M \in Mat_n(\mathbb R),b \in \mathbb{R}^n \}
